$ /var/db/repos/gentoo

`/var/db/repos/gentoo` is the locally synchronized copy of the *Gentoo ebuild directory* from the → https://gitweb.gentoo.org/repo/gentoo.git/tree[gitweb.gentoo.org] server.

This directory stores *ebuild files* which tell Portage how to build and install a package.

